---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";

const lastUpdated = "October 25, 2023";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Data Policy - Spentiva by Exyconn"
  description="Learn how we handle, store, and process your data at Spentiva."
>
  <Header />

  <div class="bg-white pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-28">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6 tracking-tight"
        >
          Data Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-text-secondary leading-relaxed"
      >
        <p class="mb-8">
          This Data Policy outlines how Spentiva by Exyconn handles your data.
          We believe in transparency and giving you control over your
          information.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mt-12 mb-6">
          1. Data Ownership
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-8">
          You own your data. We do not claim ownership over the financial data,
          personal information, or other content you provide to us. You grant us
          a license to use your data solely for the purpose of providing and
          improving our services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mt-12 mb-6">
          2. Data Storage and Processing
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-8">
          Your data is stored on secure servers located in the United States and
          other jurisdictions. We use industry-standard encryption to protect
          your data both in transit and at rest.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mt-12 mb-6">
          3. Data Retention
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-8">
          We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as needed
          to provide you services. We may also retain and use your information
          as necessary to comply with our legal obligations, resolve disputes,
          and enforce our agreements.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mt-12 mb-6">
          4. Data Deletion
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-8">
          You have the right to request the deletion of your account and
          associated data at any time. You can do this through your account
          settings or by contacting our support team. Upon request, we will
          delete your personal information from our active databases, subject to
          any legal retention requirements.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mt-12 mb-6">
          5. Data Portability
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-8">
          You have the right to export your data from our platform. We provide
          tools that allow you to download your transaction history and other
          personal information in a standard, machine-readable format.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary mt-12 mb-6">
          6. Contact Us
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-8">
          If you have any questions or concerns about our data practices, please
          contact our Data Protection Officer at:
          <br />
          <a
            href="mailto:data@spentiva.com"
            class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-500 font-medium transition-colors"
            >data@spentiva.com</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
